description: The ID of this Google Search Video module video.
name: id

description: The ID of the Google Search instance to which this Video module video belongs.
name: base_id

description: The list index of the Video module video.
name: list_index

description: The time at which this video was published.
name: time_of_publication

description: The running time (in seconds) of the video.
name: running_time

description: The image (as a Base64 string or URL) of the video.
name: image_thumbnail

description: The source URL of the video.
name: source_url

description: The URL of the video's publisher.
name: publisher_url

description: The list of images (as Base64 strings or URLs) for the markers of the video; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'markers_at_seconds', 'markers_titles', and 'markers_source_urls' fields.
name: markers_image_thumbnails

description: The list of marks (at given seconds) for the markers of the video; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'markers_image_thumbnails', 'markers_titles', and 'markers_source_urls' fields.
name: markers_at_seconds

description: The list of titles for the markers of the video; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'markers_at_seconds', 'markers_image_thumbnails', and 'markers_source_urls' fields.
name: markers_titles

description: The source URLs for the markers of the video; reconstructs a list of JSON objects with the 'markers_at_seconds', 'markers_titles', and 'markers_image_thumbnails' fields.
name: markers_source_urls
